# Applies when generating reports from JSON results

## Inputs
- Accept one or more JSON inputs; validate presence and format.
- Avoid reading all results into the chat context; compute metrics and summarize.

## Outputs
- HTML report and concise Markdown summary under `reports_YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS/`.
- Include: samples processed, throughput, ROUGE metrics (if available), runtime.

## UX
- Name files consistently; log paths; keep summaries short.

